00:02:32.125 --> 00:02:35.476
we can help to create

00:02:35.500 --> 00:02:38.809
transparency and traceability
in supply chains,

00:02:38.833 --> 00:02:42.351
and through that,
help to completely revolutionize

00:02:42.375 --> 00:02:46.958
the way that we buy
and also produce products as humans.

